Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.84,0:00:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.52,0:00:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是驚人的大翻轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.39,0:00:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登場人數是曆代最少的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清事實的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.97,0:00:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.90,0:00:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.94,0:01:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在叔叔以前學生時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.63,0:01:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做過傢庭教師的惠小姐的父母傢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.03,0:01:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了被裝置炸彈的車子爆炸了的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡的是惠小姐的妹妹寬美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲惠小姐不擅長倒車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.54,0:01:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以寬美小姐幫她倒車因而死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.82,0:02:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑犯是個叫做高橋弘昌的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和惠小姐的丈夫崎原和夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們之間有個交換殺人的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本想殺害惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來卻誤殺了寬美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來那兩個人已經認罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也以爲事件就這樣解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽狹窄的空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能輕易的倒車出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事件 還沒有結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.20,0:02:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽車爆炸事件的真相（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.38,0:02:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你怎麽突然跑開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 發生什麽事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.91,0:02:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.91,0:02:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐爲了我們特地買了蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕快去她傢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.38,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他到底在想些什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在告訴叔叔還嫌太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多掌握一些證據才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這次的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 該怎麽講好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.14,0:03:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 我已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再替我擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.31,0:03:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個紅茶 趁熱喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.72,0:03:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南也過來吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問洗手間在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.89,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是那間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.71,0:04:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崎原在二樓的書房裏特別裝了一個專用電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是用那部電話聯係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是撕掉膠佈後的痕蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.18,0:04:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那裏裝有那個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐比想象中還要有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也放心了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.39,0:05:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看她那樣子應該沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了米花車站之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有別的事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒什麽啦 不過可別太晚回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.51,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏竟然有個窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 如果從這個窗戶的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.55,0:05:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣我就了解整個情況了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就剩下證據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.79,0:06:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這次的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有幾個地方覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天惠小姐不是從超市那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狹窄的停車位倒車出來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.19,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而案發當時爲什麽要她妹妹幫她倒車出來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.83,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有惠小姐傢二樓書房裏面的電話線附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有膠佈被撕掉的痕蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏到底貼過什麽東西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.51,0:06:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.65,0:06:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 案發的那棟房子裏面有一扇秘窗你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.92,0:06:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲爆炸所以玻璃破掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然從裏面釘上了木闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過從那裏就可以看到車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不錯的設計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.83,0:07:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想說些什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.21,0:07:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說小惠和這個事件有關嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.51,0:07:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最了解她的爲人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲她是我的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.32,0:07:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔認識的是高中時代的惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.69,0:07:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入社會後 惠小姐也許改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.76,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔心裏很想這麽認爲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.11,0:07:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 事實上她已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦 上樓去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去沖涼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然講這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密的窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是我和寬美之間這樣稱呼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.57,0:08:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸以前常常在這裏看我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這裏已經很久沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小的時候我們在門前搗蛋時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常在這裏被看到而被罵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想問崎原和高橋的犯罪證物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.73,0:08:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我想看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後還有什麽新發現嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於死者寬美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽她的朋友說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.94,0:09:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在年輕的時候曾經搶過兩次惠小姐的戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是自由戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說寬美小姐是爲了好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算很文靜的惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在與崎原結婚的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.73,0:09:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也半開玩笑的告訴寬美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這次再犯 別怪我不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.99,0:09:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想叔叔應該可以找到幾個推斷的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最主要的證據…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 說不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官 剛才在電話中拜託你的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我叫高木確認過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢夥只有在那次超市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到惠小姐一次而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.19,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後他就沒在惠小姐面前出現過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時高橋的裝扮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著帽子還有墨鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利 一大早你到底怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.18,0:10:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 警官 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 終於找到證據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽意思 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸從秋葉原打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說現在要到惠小姐傢去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.00,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說只有他才能說服的了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸到底在講些什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 我們也去惠小姐傢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.49,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 爲什麽連你們也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲有點關心爸爸電話裏講的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.68,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 老師 你說有事要告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.84,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 今天我來是勸你自首的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.41,0:12:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.57,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.60,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你丈夫和你妹妹交往的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.37,0:12:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有他和高橋交換殺人的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果你就利用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將多年憎恨的妹妹給除掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把這個殺人罪嫁禍給你先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.30,0:12:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你怎麽突然這樣講呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你在兩個月前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.09,0:12:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秋葉原那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了竊聽器和自動錄音機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還嚮店員詳細的詢問使用方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是和你買的同樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竊聽器和自動錄音機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.31,0:13:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才嚮你借洗手間的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去調查過二樓的書房了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將這竊聽器裝在你丈夫的書房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷聽他和高橋之間的談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.60,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆壁旁邊留下的膠佈痕蹟就是證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一開始你是想偷聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫和你妹妹之間的談話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.07,0:13:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是後來你發現了這個秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.92,0:13:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你丈夫和不認識的男人做了交換殺人的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他也已經殺死了對方的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到你被高橋殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.13,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認爲高橋會在車子上裝置炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是裝在這個傢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你丈夫也會被懷疑因而困惑著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後你就告訴你丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.07,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要開車回父母傢去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.13,0:14:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好你妹妹的車子送去保養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以車庫是空出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫聽到這些話之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用外面的公共電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴高橋這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你不知道那個電話的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大概知道高橋不會錯過這次機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而回娘傢去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在回傢的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你不擅長倒車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.63,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你妹妹幫你把車子開出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後和計劃的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹就這樣死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.10,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了意料之外的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我突然去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.85,0:14:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚慌的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在不做的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.51,0:15:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕會被做偵探的我給揭穿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確買了竊聽器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕丈夫有外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.68,0:15:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在桌子底下裝了竊聽器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.04,0:15:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很快我就後悔 然後丟掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我根本沒用過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.90,0:15:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道外遇的對象是你妹妹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如 我是說假如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和老師推理的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會被判什麽罪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.51,0:15:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在車子裝置炸彈的是那個叫做高橋的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教唆他這麽做的人是我丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我所做的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許被裝置炸彈的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妹妹去開而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是殺人的共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是恐嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是法律部的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律師的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如你所講的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是讓你妹妹去開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.56,0:16:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點罪也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.09,0:16:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你讓機率很高肯定裝有炸彈的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你妹妹去開的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會變成殺人罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.25,0:16:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那天隨便找個借口跑到儲藏室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從窗戶那裏偷看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果和你預料的一樣 高橋走了進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將炸彈裝在車子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你確認過後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜託你妹妹幫你把車開出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在非常高的機率之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.73,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你妹妹去開裝有炸彈的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有證據說我曾經多次去看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.73,0:17:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儲藏室那個窗戶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有的話 請現在馬上拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據的話 就在叔叔的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次惠小姐在醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫的高橋先生的畫像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐說在哪裏見過他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.27,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是在傢附近的超市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲警官先生講過那個叫做高橋的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在超市跟蹤時是戴著墨鏡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽那張畫像上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有戴著墨鏡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.85,0:18:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實惠小姐在超市那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.47,0:18:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒發覺被一個叫做高橋的人跟蹤過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.88,0:18:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你之後偷聽他打電話給崎原時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.84,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才知道有這個人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽那個臉是在哪裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是在那秘密的窗戶看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 你在父母傢這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那儲藏室的窗戶偷看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.14,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在下面裝置炸彈的高橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.00,0:19:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽會知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.71,0:19:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 不想讓人看到他的高橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進入車庫前還戴著墨鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 離開車庫的時候也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.84,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 只有一次必須摘下墨鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.61,0:19:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在裝置炸彈的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.50,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲裝置炸彈這種危險的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有人戴著墨鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在漆黑的車庫裏面動手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.14,0:19:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 這張沒有戴墨鏡的畫像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.67,0:19:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你在儲藏室偷看高橋的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.08,0:20:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確偷聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.41,0:20:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想殺了我然後將保險金和父母留給我的遺産
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.49,0:20:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部拿出來給寬美做開店的資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.83,0:20:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候真的很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.46,0:20:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.47,0:20:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是最倖福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直希望回到那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.48,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.16,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年前我應該教導你一個最重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.21,0:20:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比讀書還重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.68,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣的我也和妻子分居了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.52,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也沒資格講你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在還來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.67,0:21:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著罪再次重新學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是學習如何做人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時候 你還願意教我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.03,0:23:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件解決是件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.24,0:23:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過叔叔這次好像傷得很重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.35,0:23:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.17,0:23:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是毛利偵探事務所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.18,0:23:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 洋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.50,0:23:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.52,0:23:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 演唱會嗎 我當然會去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.85,0:23:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了洋子 啦啦隊傢庭教師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.87,0:23:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麽都願意做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.84,0:23:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來根本不用我們擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.51,0:23:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真是個超快恢複精神的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.61,0:23:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得那個戴眼鏡的人
