Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.42,0:24:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 蘭 那件泳衣真大膽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.19,0:24:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子你才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.41,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開所有雜誌還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.76,0:00:25.38,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭歎息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.64,0:00:29.74,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有適合我的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.89,0:00:33.80,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.11,0:00:37.85,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都無法討得你的歡心 惹得你滿腔怒火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.64,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很抱歉如臨深淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.78,0:00:46.48,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.95,0:00:50.61,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖慾墜的感覺有什麽不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.60,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也一定要嚮前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.00,0:00:59.27,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢 一點也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.22,0:01:08.32,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到緊要關頭不出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.43,0:01:12.12,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 不要用冷淡的眼光看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.94,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我用自己的速度前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.31,0:01:20.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我馬上會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.65,0:01:24.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.14,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖慾墜的感覺有什麽不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.58,0:01:32.68,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也一定要嚮前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.00,0:01:37.31,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢 一點也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.55,0:21:47.19,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這孕育著神秘的夜裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.72,0:21:51.86,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請閉上眼睛 獻上你的祈禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.64,0:21:58.20,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這月光融融的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.77,0:22:04.62,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說我們因爲愛而生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.12,0:22:15.89,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 一切都停滯不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.50,0:22:22.18,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看未來化爲碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.46,0:22:30.89,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 赤著腳 踩在大地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.01,0:22:36.32,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越彩虹 抓住天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.10,0:22:42.84,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈禱 抓住胸前的十字架 在白天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.98,0:22:49.16,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望照燿著你 在夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.28,0:22:55.34,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖的光芒 將你擁抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.49,0:23:02.08,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠爲你停留 爲你的愛而停留
